## 🏗 High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR

A[Enterprise Data]

A --> B[Knowledge Layer]

B --> C[RAG]

C --> D[LLM]

D --> E[AI Agents]

E --> F[Enterprise Applications]
```

