# 🛠 Technology Stack

| Layer | Technologies |
|--------|--------------|
| AI | OpenAI, Azure AI, Anthropic |
| Frameworks | LangChain, LangGraph |
| Search | RAG |
| Cloud | AWS, Azure |
| Containers | Docker, Kubernetes |
| DevOps | GitHub Actions |
| Data | Vector Databases |

